# Local env files
# `.env` holds PUBLIC Vite vars only (anon keys, public URLs) — safe to commit
# so Lovable / CI builds have what they need. Real secrets (service_role,
# edge-function creds, etc.) live in Supabase edge-function secrets, not here.
# Put any developer-local overrides in `.env.local` (git-ignored below).
.env.local
.env.*.local

